track_notes: This track is an easy walk but long to reach the two summits on the edge! no difficult but if the wx is warm dont forget to bring much water! Another place to be! The landscape is wonderfull.
park at the Village of Vergons, then follow the good path to the crest, and then, just walk to the summit where is a pylone and a cross. Plenty room for antenna, and nice panorama.
May be the shorter path to summit

This track is fool... i was looking for short-cuts! Dont follow this track for the descent. There is a source at the Maison des Chasseurs. park at the village Morgon. Plenty room on summit (tree little pylone). No trees for antenna
A bit hard and long, but it disurb 6 points.
For healthy walkers... very hot in summer, can be done in bonus season if no snow. Better to have a GPS and follow the track.
